http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/HC-rejects-Nisham%E2%80%99s-plea/article13983873.ece

The Kerala High Court on Tuesday rejected a plea by Mohammed Nisham, accused in the Chandrabose murder case, for summoning certain mediapersons and examining them in the case.Justice B. Kemal Pasha, however, permitted the accused to examine the investigation officer and sub inspector of police Peramangalam in connection with the case.As for summoning editors of newspapers and other media, the court was of the view that the petitioner could not be permitted to press into service reports as evidence.